Class EosioJavaRpcProviderImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • one.block.eosiojavarpcprovider.implementations.EosioJavaRpcProviderImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    one.block.eosiojava.interfaces.IRPCProvider

    public class EosioJavaRpcProviderImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements one.block.eosiojava.interfaces.IRPCProvider
    Simple implementation of an RPC provider for communicating with the blockchain. The calls are implemented synchronously. It is assumed that the developer will wrap them in asynchronous semantics such as AsyncTask in normal use...
